OL,3,CGrandmother's 'treasured items' binned
OL,4,Cby contractors who 'thought she was
OL,5,Cdead'
OL,7,FAn elderly widow from the Isle of
OL,8,FWight has lost her treasured
OL,9,Fpossessions after they were thrown
OL,10,Faway by contractors who wrongly
OL,11,Fbelieved she was dead.
OL,13,FMabel Ogle fell at her home in October
OL,14,Flast year, and was moved to a respite
OL,15,Fcare centre whilst she recovered.
OL,17,FDuring her time at the site, her house
OL,18,Fflooded, and contractors were given
OL,19,Fpermission to enter the property to
OL,20,Fassess the damage.
