OL,3,CGrandmother's 'treasured items' binned
OL,4,Cby contractors who 'thought she was
OL,5,Cdead'
OL,7,FThey were told to remove damaged
OL,8,Ffurniture, but instead removed almost
OL,9,Feverything from the property and
OL,10,Fbinned it.
OL,12,FMabel's family say they haven't been
OL,13,Fable to break the news to her that
OL,14,Fsome of her most prized possessions,
OL,15,Fincluding her wedding photos and war
OL,16,Fmedials, have been lost forever.
OL,18,FKaren Henshaw, Mabel's granddaughter,
OL,19,Ftold ITV Meridian they can never tell
OL,20,Fher what has happened as it will break
OL,21,Fher heart.
