OL,3,CGrandmother's 'treasured items' binned
OL,4,Cby contractors who 'thought she was
OL,5,Cdead'
OL,7,F"She's lost all of life's
OL,8,Fpossessions," she said.
OL,10,F"My poor nan is totally unaware. The
OL,11,Fcarers are still going in six times a
OL,12,Fday. And she's got nothing but the bed
OL,13,Fand a few clothes that she's wearing.
OL,15,F"Everything's gone.
OL,17,F"It's like... all the things that I
OL,18,Fwant to pass down to my grandchildren.
OL,19,FI've got nothing now.
